            <title>古尔曼：苹果正为 watchOS 27 测试全新模块化表盘，2026 款“彩虹”产品本月发布</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/946/192.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/946/192.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
